Notes: Holiday Inn Express Thanksgiving Classic...UWL starts game on 10-0 run...SC
opens 2nd quarter on 21-3 run to lead 32-20...UWL goes on 10-0 run to cut lead
to 32-30...SC leads 54-44, UWL goes on 21-2 run...Schoenenberger (UWL) ties
school record w/ 6 three-pointers...Morrow (SC) 22 points, 19 rebounds.
